I don't even leave my desk.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:26.530
Like the mailman comes,
and I put my feet up

00:11:26.530 --> 00:11:28.950
because I'm like, don't look
at me through the window.

00:11:28.950 --> 00:11:29.491
I'm not here.

00:11:29.491 --> 00:11:31.582
I don't exist.

00:11:31.582 --> 00:11:34.660
So I was like, I need
to get a service animal.

